## Cohort Analysis Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define cohorts: Choose the cohort dimension (acquisition date, source, campaign, etc.)
- [ ] 2. Choose metrics: DAU, retention, revenue, LTV per cohort
- [ ] 3. Build cohort table: Plot cohorts over time with the chosen metric
- [ ] 4. Identify patterns: Where do cohorts diverge? What's driving differences?
- [ ] 5. Segment: Break cohorts into sub-groups to find root causes
- [ ] 6. Recommend: Actionable steps to improve underperforming cohorts

## Key Inputs
- Cohort dimension: {{cohort_dimension}}
- Metrics to analyze: {{metrics}}
- Time period: {{time_period}}
- Data sources: {{data_sources}}
